! Krystal - Horizontal Story River

This plugin is an attempt to bring [[Andy Matuschak's Evergreen notes|https://notes.andymatuschak.org/]] system into [[TiddlyWiki|https://tiddlywiki.com/]] that I found after reading articles by [[Anne-Laure Le Cunff|https://nesslabs.com/]].

Thanks both for the inspiration, my (thinking about) notes finally started to become (somehow) useful!

!! Features

* horizontal story view for tiddlers (show [[Example]] ğŸ‘‰)
* bi-directional links at the bottom of each tiddler
* closing open tiddlers to the right (customizable in [[plugin settings|$:/plugins/rmnvsl/krystal/settings]])
* customizable header instead of sidebar (use tag {{$:/plugins/rmnvsl/krystal/header||$:/core/ui/TagTemplate}} to add new content)
* nice animations and transitions ğŸ®

!! Installation

You can either:

* save this whole ~TiddlyWiki by clicking the save button {{$:/core/ui/Buttons/save-wiki}}, or
* add just the ''bare'' plugin by dragging the following link onto your project [[$:/plugins/rmnvsl/krystal]]

